<p class="tv-widget-idea__description-row tv-widget-idea__description-row--clamped js-widget-idea__popup" data-href="/chart/AUDJPY/NcJXQ3sI-Market-Structure-Simplified/">
It is easy to get confused with overflowing information about market structure in the trading world.

To simplify things we have come up with a way of analysing market structure simply by marking each high or low.

In this particular example, you can see that higher lows were being created all the way down the bearish trend, so we knew that it was a seller&#x27;s...
</p>

<p class="tv-widget-idea__description-row tv-widget-idea__description-row--clamped js-widget-idea__popup" data-href="/chart/AMAT/gjugg1kV-Key-Ideas-to-trade-big-daily-structures-Example-on-AMAT/">
I will keep this post short, so you can get a general idea of this trading style.

First of all , we have a situation where the price could not make a new ATH in 200 days. It&#x27;s important to notice that we can draw a clear structure with well-defined limits because the price stayed in a clear range between 146 and 114

Now that the structure is clear, it is easy...

<p class="tv-widget-idea__description-row tv-widget-idea__description-row--clamped js-widget-idea__popup" data-href="/chart/BTCUSD/Z2mjbvbO-Bitcoin-Bulls-need-price-back-above-60k/">
After reaching the recent ATH near 68k, Bitcoin has started to correct.
This correction is normal and shouldn&#x27;t be a concern for long time holders.
The drop from the top is also corrective in nature...
At this moment the price is under 60k support and, for a signal that the correction is over, bulls need to drive the price back above. In this instance we can...
</p>

<p class="tv-widget-idea__description-row tv-widget-idea__description-row--clamped js-widget-idea__popup" data-href="/chart/GBPJPY/RrqPP3Ey-GBPJPY-ABC-Correction-Time-To-Buy-Again/">
On the daily chart , the price created a strong impulsive wave.
Considering this we need to suppose that the correction should no be very deep.
Usually, it takes the shape of a &quot;Bullish Flag&quot; or a &quot;Falling Wedge&quot; pattern.
On the 4-hour chart, the price is creating a potential ABC correction wave.
The support area is located between 155.50 - 155.80. Here we need...

<p class="tv-widget-idea__description-row tv-widget-idea__description-row--clamped js-widget-idea__popup" data-href="/chart/AMAT/gjugg1kV-Key-Ideas-to-trade-big-daily-structures-Example-on-AMAT/">
I will keep this post short, so you can get a general idea of this trading style.

First of all , we have a situation where the price could not make a new ATH in 200 days. It&#x27;s important to notice that we can draw a clear structure with well-defined limits because the price stayed in a clear range between 146 and 114

Now that the structure is clear, it is easy...
</p>

<p class="tv-widget-idea__description-row tv-widget-idea__description-row--clamped js-widget-idea__popup" data-href="/chart/XAUUSD/9njHuDgn-GOLD-Anyone-Else-Notice-This/">
Gold has been making some interesting price action.

We can see that previously Gold created an impulse (1) and then a bullish correction (2) which lead to an ascending correction (3) before it came tumbling down.

Gold is making almost the identical price action now. We had the impulse and the bullish correction, and now we&#x27;re currently in an ascending...
</p>

<p class="tv-widget-idea__description-row tv-widget-idea__description-row--clamped js-widget-idea__popup" data-href="/chart/NFLX/k9zSChIR-The-Squid-Game-Shows-Why-Most-People-Don-t-Make-Money-Trading/">
Squid game is the hottest series on Netflix ($NFLX) right now, in which 456 players join a game of death, where they have a chance to win 456 Billion Korean Won (KRW), or 38.5 Milllion US Dollars.

What’s interesting about this series is that it depicts human sentiment in a very realistic way. We could see how market participants think and act by looking at the...

Hello everyone:

Today I want to discuss a topic in Risk Management, specifically on when and how to move your STOP LOSS to BREAKEVEN or in PROFIT when you have a running profit trade/position.

In an impulsive phase of the market, we want to make sure to protect our entry as well as secure profits.

In this example of EURUSD, I managed to get 2 entries in, and...

<p class="tv-widget-idea__description-row tv-widget-idea__description-row--clamped js-widget-idea__popup" data-href="/chart/BTCUSD/9y8YvC34-PRICE-ACTION-TRADING-RISING-WEDGE-PATTERN/">

Hey traders,

Rising wedge pattern is one of the most accurate price action patterns.
Being relatively simple to recognize, it is applied in various trading strategies.

⭐️The pattern itself signifies the exhaustion of bulls.
Even though the asset keeps growing in value, the price action legs contract forming a narrowing...
</p>

<p class="tv-widget-idea__description-row tv-widget-idea__description-row--clamped js-widget-idea__popup" data-href="/script/tNG177SV-Realtime-5D-Profile-LucF/">
█  OVERVIEW

This indicator displays a realtime profile that can be configured to visualize five dimensions: ​volume, price, time, activity and age. For each price level in a bar or timeframe, you can display total or delta ​volume or ticks. The tick count measures activity on a level. The thickness of each level&#x27;s line indicates its age, which helps you identify...
</p>

<p class="tv-widget-idea__description-row tv-widget-idea__description-row--clamped js-widget-idea__popup" data-href="/script/UkaoD896-Divergence-Support-Resistence/">
Another script based on zigzag, divergence, and to yield support and resistence levels.

This idea started with below two concepts:

▶ Support and resistence are simply levels where price has rejected to go further down or up. Usually, we can derive this based on pivots. But, if we start looking at every pivot, there will be many of them and may be confusing to...
</p>
